Home Intensive Care Inc&lt;KDNY> said holders of 431,093 shares of its callablecumulative convertible preferred of the 499,500 outstandingwere exercised their conversion right prior to the end of thecompany's offer of 2.2 common shares for each preferred.    It said holders of the remaining preferred have the optionof converting their stock for two common shares until March 5,1988.    The company said conversion of the preferred will result inannual dividend savings of 431,093 dlrs. Reuter&#3;